Date: 4 - 5 December 2018 Venue: RWTH Aachen University, Germany Website The Institute for Advanced Mining Technologies is presenting a new international conference on High Performance Mining. The Conference provides a platform for international mining operators, suppliers, and experts from research and industry to discuss challenges and best practices in achieving high productivity and high performance in open pit and underground mining. The High Performance Mining Conference will look at different levers for improving productivity to achieve high performance mining in today’s changing and challenging socio-economic environment.